{"id": "23401", "post": "<div class=\"post-23401 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-community-news tag-hostworld\" id=\"post-23401\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/community-news-hostworld-announces-us-expansion-exclusive-offers-included/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Community News: Hostworld Announces US-Expansion \u2013 Exclusive Offers Included</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/community-news/\" rel=\"tag\">community news</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hostworld/\" rel=\"tag\">hostworld</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> July 22, 2020 @ 7:27 am, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMjQ1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDE2IDI0NSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" title=\"Interesting Web Hosting and VPS Hosting Community News\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Interesting-Industry-News-LEB.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Interesting Web Hosting and VPS Hosting Community News\" width=\"416\" height=\"245\"></a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As part of </span><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/looking-for-community-industry-news/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">LowEndBox\u2019s new \u201cinteresting news\u201d series</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, we received a submission from <a href=\"https://hostworld.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hostworld</a> about their recent expansion outside of the UK to Chicago in the United States! Hostworld has been featured a <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/?s=hostworld&amp;searchsubmit=Find\">few times on LowEndBox recently</a> and they are an <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/hostworld\">active member of LowEndTalk</a> so we are happy to share their exciting news.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><b>Here is the announcement piece we received from them:</b></p><p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201c</span>hostworld.uk have now branched out from the UK and are now offering VPS services in the US from Chicago! </em><em>Customers can deploy the same suite of VPS plans in both the UK and US as all of the plans are identical in specifications and pricing to make choosing a VPS package as easy as possible.</em></p><p><em>We have not only expanded our location offering, but for the first time, we\u2019ve launched NVMe based storage at our US location too. Whilst we only currently offer NVMe storage at our US data centre, be rest assured we are working hard to bring NVMe storage to our UK nodes and we will shortly be launching NVMe in the UK. </em><em>You can see our US NVMe VPS packages here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hostworld.uk/nvme-vps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://hostworld.uk/nvme-vps</a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201c</span></em></p><p><b>And for the exclusive launch offers:</b></p><p><strong>US Launch Special 1</strong><br>\n768MB RAM<br>\n1x vCPU<br>\n15GB NVMe Storage<br>\nFREE 45GB Backup Storage<br>\nUnmetered Bandwidth<br>\nFast 1 Gbps Uplink<br>\nIPv4 &amp; IPv6<br>\n<a href=\"https://portal.hostworld.uk/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=78\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Only \u00a32.49 ($3.03) per month</a></p><p><strong>US Launch Special 2</strong><br>\n2GB RAM<br>\n2x vCPU<br>\n30GB NVMe Storage<br>\nFREE 90GB Backup Storage<br>\nUnmetered Bandwidth<br>\nFast 1 Gbps Uplink<br>\nIPv4 &amp; IPv6<br>\n<a href=\"https://portal.hostworld.uk/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=79\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Only \u00a34.89 ($5.95) per month</a></p><p><strong>We are always looking for interesting community news! </strong></p><p>Are you a hosting provider, VPN provider, or similar with interesting industry news? We\u2019d like to hear from you. You can do so easily, either by <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/jbiloh\">sending us a message directly</a> on LowEndTalk or by submitting a ticket on our <a href=\"https://lowendbox.freshdesk.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">helpdesk</a>.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fcommunity-news-hostworld-announces-us-expansion-exclusive-offers-included%2F&amp;t=Community%20News%3A%20Hostworld%20Announces%20US-Expansion%20-%20Exclusive%20Offers%20Included\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Community%20News%3A%20Hostworld%20Announces%20US-Expansion%20-%20Exclusive%20Offers%20Included&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fcommunity-news-hostworld-announces-us-expansion-exclusive-offers-included%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-netwo